{"tid":2131690,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警反送中拘9,216人 僅兩成檢控被轟濫捕  議員：差人暴行引發示威","createTime":"2020-07-30T04:24:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T04:51:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ef2632416ea64fc528c7efd10cbaf4f5621a5ce2","tid":2131690,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:24:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/OC4SMPLCDGCR5LBAMPGPW5WMX4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2FOC4SMPLCDGCR5LBAMPGPW5WMX4%2F&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhCLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=d86ac9ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2FOC4SMPLCDGCR5LBAMPGPW5WMX4%2F&h=2036beb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/OC4SMPLCDGCR5LBAMPGPW5WMX4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警反送中拘9,216人 僅兩成檢控被轟濫捕 <br />\n議員：差人暴行引發示威<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/caKzirproJaZvw03VQwQCQWEHt0=/190x112/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/T3VWQVYGGBUDTVL4L3BTP3INEI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcaKzirproJaZvw03VQwQCQWEHt0%3D%2F190x112%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FT3VWQVYGGBUDTVL4L3BTP3INEI.jpg&h=41498d09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反修例運動以來逾九千人被捕，但僅兩成人被控。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】反送中運動至今逾一年，警方公佈相關被捕人數多達9,216人，當中1,972人遭檢控，檢控比率為21.4%，653人被控暴動罪。另外今年上半年，全港錄得32,345宗罪案，較去年同期增加27.9%。公民黨楊岳橋批評警方濫捕，質疑警察「好多時拉咗先算」，「根本就係警暴為市民所不齒，先引致更多人上街示威」。<br />\n<br />\n截至今年上半年，涉反送中運動被捕。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n四成為學生<br />\n<br />\n警方又指，因反送中被捕人士中，有3,725名學生，佔全部被捕人40.4%，大專生和中學生分別佔五成半和四成半。<br />\n<br />\n另外，警方今年上半年在全港錄得32,345宗罪案，較去年同期的25,295宗增加7,050宗，升幅27.9%。暴。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨楊岳橋回應警方數字，指很多案件屬濫捕，警察「好多時拉咗先算」。他指出，很多案件顯示警方無法滿足法庭毫無合理疑點的要求，而警方稱反送中破壞治安更是掩耳盜鈴，「根本就係警暴為市民所不齒，先引致更多人上街示威」。公民黨譚文豪亦批評，警員在抗爭案經常有不可信及自相矛盾的證供，但從不自我檢討，相信「如果警方查返自己人，罪案數字將以幾何級數上升」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DjtpgQ_tjWRqxCvBXASFyPdkFSM=/438x454/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YW2DO5V54PSIFHKS5MSRG7VLFY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDjtpgQ_tjWRqxCvBXASFyPdkFSM%3D%2F438x454%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYW2DO5V54PSIFHKS5MSRG7VLFY.gif&h=60cf3e86&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8e31430cdef16a4f684615cae8264ffccb2e3ad","tid":2131690,"uid":180851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:25:45.000Z","msg":"成班垃圾IQ又低 EQ又低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52833f5f0b5049590230db04023027606b2e1fe4","tid":2131690,"uid":100772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:27:41.000Z","msg":"邊止9千幾人<br />\n一開頭已經話咁既數 之後一直冇加<br />\n仲不停日日大圍捕  下下幾百人都話係停係9千幾人"},{"pid":"0c299aa00df5ed19c86d85d3a61c5639783847d5","tid":2131690,"uid":352564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:51:03.000Z","msg":"上年12月份數字係8900人左右，之後拉幾多大家心裡有數"}]}